drivel: drivel (GNOME Journal Editor)
drivel:
drivel: Drivel is a GNOME client for working with online journals, also known 
drivel: as weblogs or simply blogs. It retains a simple and elegant design 
drivel: while providing many powerful features, including support for
drivel: LiveJournal, Blogger, MovableType, Advogato, and Atom journals (like
drivel: WordPress and Drupal), offline composition and editing, and journal
drivel: system extensions, including LiveJournal security groups and 
drivel: MovableType categories.
